{"id":13257,"slug":"kiesgrube-weich-2","url":"https://www.hejfish.com/d/13257-kiesgrube-weich-2","name":"Kiesgrube Weich 2","seo_name":"Kiesgrube Weich 2","description":"<p>Die Grube bietet meist schlammigen Untergrund, nur vereinzelt findet man an den Uferbereichen ein paar feste Stellen. Unterwasser gibt es keine markanten Punkte wie Kanten oder Plateaus. Fischbestand ist gut und man fängt alle Arten des Besatzes. Die Ufer sind steil, außer an zwei Plätzen am vorderen und hinteren Eck der Grube. Größe ca. 1ha und Tiefen von 1 bis 2,6 Meter. </p>","intro":"","details":"","borders":"<p>Kiesgrube Weich 2 zwischen Luhe und Diebrunn an der Staatstraße 2657. Gewässertafeln/Beschilderungen an den einzelnen Kiesgruben beachten. Das gesamte Gewässer darf befischt werden.</p>","image":"https://file.hejfish.com/image/cc1200x900/27/8d/278dc7e3d899a415ca11af9a5fcee15a0266bc2f.jpeg","water_size_ha":null,"fish":["Hecht","Zander","Wels","Aal","Karpfen","Schleie","Rotauge","Rotfeder","Brasse"],"techniques":["Ansitzangeln","Feedern","Posenangeln","Spinnangeln"],"properties":[],"water_type":"See","rules_text":"","rules_files":[],"tickets":[],"ticket_types":[],"manager":{"id":1797,"name":"Sportanglerbund Wernberg-Köblitz e. V.","street":"Kärntnerstraße 8","postal_code":"92533","city":"Wernberg-Köblitz","telephone":"","email":"","website":"http://www.sab-wernberg.de","logo":"https://file.hejfish.com/image/r200x200/d3/66/d3668bd4f68a2349b79c3d2d5171b30ebf4a6a1c.jpeg","slug":"sportanglerbund-wernberg-koeblitz-e-v"},"season_begin":"0001-01-01","season_end":"0001-12-31","features":{"accessible":false,"public_transport":false,"boat":false,"belly_boat":false,"digital_ticket":true,"night_fishing":true,"ice_fishing":false,"depth_map":false,"has_gauges":false},"location":{"city":{"id":34695,"name":"Wernberg-Köblitz"},"district":{"id":455,"name":"Kreis Schwandorf"},"state":{"id":10,"name":"Bayern","slug":"bayern"},"country":{"id":2,"name":"Deutschland","code":"de","slug":"deutschland"}},"produc